videoDetails.shortDescription:
Ciao Pandas! 
Today we will Learn Spanish with NARCOS and we will learn Spanish Colombian accent. 

As you know, here on PolylgotPanda we love the idea of immersion and we cant promote enough how good is to learn Spanish with movies and films. So our goal is to bring you the best Spanish movies to learn Spanish. 

0:00 INTRO 
1:49 PART 1: Watch the Clip with Subtitles 
2:45 PART 2: Learn Vocab/Grammar/Slang from the Clip 
13:01 PART 3: Watch the Clip Without Subtitles 
13:57 FINAL  

Our videos are made for everyone: beginners, intermediate and advanced. If you like this video, remember that here on PolyglotPanda you can find thousands of videos to learn Spanish from movies so you can hear real Spanish spoken by native people. 


In this channel, you will learn how to speak Spanish like a native through conversation and real slang. It's time to improve your vocabulary and fluency with PolyglotPanda. 


For more information: www.poylgotpanda.com

Follow the journey of the Polyglot Panda and discover how to learn a language! This is, by far, the best way to learn a language! Subscribe and be part of the Panda Family! 

www.polyglotpanda.com
